<br>
I rewrote the scripts for fun and had one that selected a single target for everyone and then used an assist-until-dead approach.  With that AI, even my small 3-PC group would mow down most anything at max difficulty without me having to intervene.  This is a 5000 year old tactic that for some reason still hasn't made it into RPGs.<br>
